videos.description: Ben Humphreys sacks Clayton Thorson to force a three and out on first drive of game.
videos.headline: Humphreys sacks Thorson on 3rd down

videos.description: Riley Lees makes toe tapping catch on the sideline to help set up a field goal.
videos.headline: Riley Lees sideline catch helps set up Wildcats field goal

videos.description: Montre Hartage makes a diving interception on Daniel Jones' pass to end the Blue Devils drive.
videos.headline: Hartage intercepts Jones

videos.description: Daniel Jones scores the Blue Devils' first touchdown of the game with a 11-yard run.
videos.headline: Jones runs for 11-yard TD

videos.description: Jared McGee gets ejected for a targeting penalty in the first quarter.
videos.headline: McGee ejected for targeting

videos.description: Duke's Alonzo Saxton II rips ball away from  Cameron Green to force a turnover.
videos.headline: Saxton rips ball away from Green

videos.description: Daniel Jones powers though defenders to score the Blue Devils' third touchdown.
videos.headline: Jones 4-yard TD run extends Duke's lead

videos.description: Kyke Queiro forces Brittain Brown to fumble, Paddy Fisher recovers for the Wildcats
videos.headline: Wildcats force fumble

videos.description: Justin Jackson runs it in for Northwestern's first touchdown of the afternoon late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Jackson scores Wildcats' first TD

videos.description: Duke's Mark Gilbert makes a nice play to intercept Clayton Thorson
videos.headline: Gilbert dives to pick off Thorson

videos.description: Daniel Jones passes to Davis Koppenhaver to extend the Blue Devils' lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Jones hits Koppenhaver for his 2nd TD pass of the day

videos.description: Shaun Wilson adds to the Blue Devils' lead with eight yard run in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Wilson runs for 8-yard TD

videos.description: Mark Gilbert picks off Clayton Thorson for the second time in the game.
videos.headline: Gilbert snags another interception

videos.description: Backup QB Matt Alviti hits Riley Lees in the back of the end zone for a 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Lees snags TD in back of end zone

videos.description: Daniel Jones comments on his teams winning performance and his four touchdown game.
videos.headline: QB Daniel Jones on Duke's win
